&lt;p>Pratibimba got a temporary power &lt;br>
A power to travel the time &lt;br>
and then make others to travel the time along with him &lt;br>
At that very moment, Pratibimba chose to travel to Treta Yuga &lt;br>
He met Raavana, &lt;br>
This is the time Raavana is in war with Rama &lt;br>
But not killed in the hands of Rama. &lt;br>
Pratibimba brought him along with him to the twenty-first century.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>